    }
  },
  {
    "type": "NarrativeText",
    "element_id": "5bbd7c8a7f8957a6d7a15278f019081f",
    "text": "Where the projections are parameter matrices W.2 \u20ac Rte, WE E RtwowrXde WV \u00a9 Remote Xde and WO \u20ac Rls x dons,",
